title: Hoover WindTunnel Troubleshooting: WindTunnel Air Brush Roll
description: If the brush roll on your Hoover Air vacuum won't spin or has suddenly stopped spinning, there are a few quick steps you can take to troubleshoot the problem. In this short tutorial, we'll show you how to get your WindTunnel Air brush roll spinning again.
